            <event type="researchStep">
               <head xml:lang="en">Obtain the informed consent of participants</head>
               <head xml:lang="fr">Obtenir le consentement éclairé des participants</head>
               <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">Seek consent of the participants by advising them about
      risks and benefits of research participation and data sharing. Inform them how research data
      will be stored, preserved and used in the long-term, and how confidentiality can be protected
      when needed.</desc>
